OL,3,GStrathclyde
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA mainly dry
OL,6,Fstart to the evening with just the odd
OL,7,Fshower. More persistent rain and
OL,8,Fdrizzle then spreading to Argyll and
OL,9,Fwest coast during the evening pushing
OL,10,Finland tonight and turning heavier at
OL,11,Ftimes.
OL,12,
OL,13,CMonday:FA cloudy day with outbreaks of
OL,14,Frain some of which will be heavy at
OL,15,Ftimes, but there should be a few drier
OL,16,Finterludes too, especially later.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
